<package version="1.0">
  <name>HTML_Common</name>
  <summary>PEAR::HTML_Common is a base class for other HTML classes.</summary>
  <description>
The PEAR::HTML_Common package provides methods for html code display and attributes handling.
* Methods to set, remove, update html attributes.
* Handles comments in HTML code.
* Handles layout and tabs for nicer HTML code.
